            {
              "mark": "A1",
              "note": "$t = 1$"
            },
            {
              "mark": "A1",
              "note": "$t = 3$ (seconds)"
            }
          ],
          "answer": "$t = 1$ s and $t = 3$ s",
          "solution": "**Plan:** the particle is at rest when $v = 0$.$$3t^2 - 12t + 9 = 3(t - 1)(t - 3) = 0 \\Rightarrow t = 1 \\text{ or } t = 3$$",
          "verify": [
            "Eq(3*1**2 - 12*1 + 9, 0)",
            "Eq(3*3**2 - 12*3 + 9, 0)"
          ]
        },
        {
          "label": "b",
